attributes.additional_details:
Refugees must be Processed under the 'Convention relating to the Status of Refugees' www.ohchr.org/EN/ProfessionalInterest/Pages/StatusOfRefugees.aspx  A Refugee will abide by Ch 1, Art 2 - General Obligations;
"Every refugee has duties to the country in which he finds himself, which require in particular that he conform to its laws and regulations as well as to measures taken for the maintenance of public order".
Compliance with the 'Convention relating to the Status of Refugees' is required.
